T*
(- Gravity should first be understood as a scientific principle before it is treated as) Tj
T*
(an exam topic.) Tj
T*
(- The learner must understand gravitational attraction, mass, and weight because it) Tj
T*
(controls how questions in Gravity are answered correctly.) Tj
T*
