T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on distinguishing between mass and weight on Earth.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in gravitational attraction, mass, and weight that the) Tj
T*
(question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Gravity step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
